There's one way to sum up what we believe at PhoenixTeam - time is of the essence. Mortgage technology delivery is unique. The intense pressure to deliver a digital customer experience, while also meeting regulatory requirements, while also reducing operational expense, and also reducing the cost to originate the loan... It goes on and on. Does your team have a sense of urgency? Are you sure they are working on the right things? How do you know the teams can deliver the outcomes you need? Are your teams telling you the problems? Are they able to detect and escalate the right issues? You can count on PhoenixTeam to get to the heart of the matter quickly and help you get the mortgage technology outcomes you need .Read More
